Class Match

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.common.utils.observe.MessageObservable
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.Match
All Implemented Interfaces:
EndGameConditionsObserver
Direct Known Subclasses:
SoloMatch
public class Match
extends MessageObservable
implements EndGameConditionsObserver
This class represents the a match of the game, it coordinates the players and their turns. The controller interacts with the model by the methods of this class
